com.vernalis.pdbconnector2.query

Class RCSBQueryRunner

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vernalis.pdbconnector2.query.RCSBQueryRunner

  • public class RCSBQueryRunner
extends java.lang.Object
    Class to run an RCSB Query. The class should be instantiated with a query model, and any non-default parameters set via the corresponding setter methods.
    Since:
    1.28.0
    Author:
    S.Roughley knime@vernalis.com
